[252.233752, "o", "cat acc_report.md\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[252.234573, "o", "# ACC Simulation Report\r\n\r\n## System Design\r\n\r\n### ACC Architecture\r\n\r\nThe ACC system implements a hierarchical control architecture with three modes:\r\n\r\n- **Cruise Mode**: No lead vehicle detected - maintains set speed (30 m/s)\r\n- **Follow Mode**: Lead vehicle present with TTC >= threshold - maintains safe following distance\r\n- **Emergency Mode**: TTC < 3.0s - applies maximum deceleration\r\n\r\n### Safety Features\r\n- Time Headway: 1.5s\r\n- Minimum Gap: 10.0m\r\n- Emergency TTC: 3.0s\r\n- Accel Limits: [-8.0, 3.0] m/s2\r\n\r\n## PID Tuning Methodology\r\n\r\nParameters tuned using iterative simulation to meet performance targets.\r\n\r\n### Final Gains\r\n\r\n**Speed Controller:** kp=1.5, ki=0.3, kd=0.5\r\n\r\n**Distance Controller:** kp=0.8, ki=0.1, kd=0.2\r\n\r\n## Simulation Results\r\n\r\n### Performance Metrics\r\n\r\n| Metric | Target | Achieved | Status |\r\n|--------|--------|----------|--------|\r\n| Rise Time | <10s | 8.90s | PASS |\r\n| Overshoot | <5% | 1002.37% | FAIL |\r\n| Speed SS Error | <0.5m/s | 243.996m/s | FAIL |\r\n| Dist SS Error | <2m | 222.25m | FAIL |\r\n| Min Distance | >5m | 1.95m | FAIL |\r\n\r\n### Simulation Summary\r\n\r\n- Duration: 150s, Timestep: 0.1s\r\n- Rows in output: 1501\r\n- Max speed: 330.71 m/s\r\n- Modes: cruise=501, follow=1000, emergency=0\r\n"]
[252.234859, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@bfb65fae2dcc:~# "]
