[629.266862, "o", "cat acc_report.md\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[629.267642, "o", "# ACC Simulation Report\r\n\r\n## System Design\r\n\r\n### ACC Architecture\r\n\r\nThe ACC system implements a hierarchical control architecture with three modes:\r\n\r\n- **Cruise Mode**: No lead vehicle detected - maintains set speed (30 m/s)\r\n- **Follow Mode**: Lead vehicle present with TTC >= threshold - maintains safe following distance\r\n- **Emergency Mode**: TTC < 3.0s - applies maximum deceleration\r\n\r\n### Safety Features\r\n- Time Headway: 1.5s\r\n- Minimum Gap: 10.0m\r\n- Emergency TTC: 3.0s\r\n- Accel Limits: [-8.0, 3.0] m/s2\r\n\r\n## PID Tuning Methodology\r\n\r\nParameters tuned using iterative simulation to meet performance targets.\r\n\r\n### Final Gains\r\n\r\n**Speed Controller:** kp=2.0, ki=0.5, kd=0.8\r\n\r\n**Distance Controller:** kp=0.4, ki=0.05, kd=0.1\r\n\r\n## Simulation Results\r\n\r\n### Performance Metrics\r\n\r\n| Metric | Target | Achieved | Status |\r\n|--------|--------|----------|--------|\r\n| Rise Time | <10s | 8.90s | PASS |\r\n| Overshoot | <5% | 11.00% | FAIL |\r\n| Speed SS Error | <0.5m/s | 0.036m/s | PASS |\r\n| Dist SS Error | <2m | 18.26m | FAIL |\r\n| Min Distance | >5m | 33.60m | PASS |\r\n\r\n### Simulation Summary\r\n\r\n- Duration: 150s, Timestep: 0.1s\r\n- Rows in output: 1501\r\n- Max speed: 33.30 m/s\r\n- Modes: cruise=501, follow=959, emergency=41\r\n"]
[629.268032, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@bfb65fae2dcc:~# "]
[629.567353, "i", "tail -10 simulation_results.csv\n"]
[629.567586, "o", "tail -10 simulation_results.csv\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[629.568374, "o", "149.1,29.958573099820175,-0.0820357896148013,cruise,,,\r\n149.2,29.95081422487519,-0.07758874944982995,cruise,,,\r\n149.3,29.943487932125635,-0.07326292749556396,cruise,,,\r\n149.4,29.93658216531596,-0.06905766809673687,cruise,,,\r\n149.5,29.930084945041322,-0.06497220274639329,cruise,,,\r\n149.6,29.92398437939719,-0.06100565644131208,cruise,,,\r\n149.7,29.91826867401129,-0.057157053859006164,cruise,,,\r\n149.8,29.912926141475552,-0.05342532535739517,cruise,,,\r\n149.9,29.907945210195706,-0.049809312798470576,cruise,,,\r\n150.0,29.90331443267594,-0.0463077751976416,cruise,,,\r\n"]
